		<div id="comment_body_64298337"><p><div class="quote"><p>Do you really think Apple has an obligation to support and promote <i>all</i> forms of marketing and advertising in direct competition from within their own house?</p></div><p>Yup, they do have an obligation.  That's a consequence of being part of a duopoly which squeezed out all the competition from the mobile OS market.  If you don't want to be treated like a cartel, don't become one.</p></div>
	</div>

